It’s a part of me 📸🤎

Stepping in front of the lens with my good friend @victoriasirakovaphotographer  was so much fun! I always learn so much when modeling and posing for photos. It teaches me how to better relate to my clients and feel those vulnerabilities that come with the photoshoot experience. I have a lot of appreciation for everyone who has given me their trust to share their vision with me and to be vulnerable in the process of making them come to life. That’s the magic ✨📸🙌

Its been a month ✨
 
  My billboard was a neighbor to some of the most powerful companies like @netflix and @ktla5news. 

  And here is it, my birthday present this year, reminds me that the sky is the limit, and what do you wish for in the bottom of your 🫀, can become reality, if you work hard for it and believe in yourself! 

  Forever thankful for the models and the team helping me to have this beautiful billboard. And to my husband @thisisgeee, who always supports my dreams! 

  Thank you!

What exactly is a group branding shoot?
It's one shoot day with multiple brands getting their content shot together! So why would you want to do this?
It lowers costs immensely as you're splitting the costs of location, models, production, and design with other brands. Plus, you have other brands repping your products in their photos! =)
This is something that we're slowly introducing and would love to know what you think about this kind of shoot! (ad Aa
